title: Complete Web Development Bootcamp
description: Learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React and Node.js to become a full-stack web developer.
learningOutcomes: Build responsive websites using HTML, CSS and Bootstrap
Create dynamic web applications with JavaScript and React
Develop backend APIs with Node.js and Express
Deploy full-stack applications to production servers

title: Data Science and Machine Learning
description: Master the skills of data analysis, visualization and machine learning with Python.
learningOutcomes: Analyze and visualize data using Python libraries like Pandas and Matplotlib
Build machine learning models with scikit-learn and TensorFlow
Apply statistical methods to extract insights from datasets
Develop end-to-end data science projects

title: UX/UI Design Fundamentals
description: Learn the principles of user experience and interface design for digital products.
learningOutcomes: Create user personas and journey maps
Design wireframes and prototypes for web and mobile applications
Conduct usability testing and gather user feedback
Develop a portfolio of UX/UI design projects

title: Advanced JavaScript: From Zero to Hero
description: Deep dive into modern JavaScript with ES6+, async/await, and more advanced concepts.
learningOutcomes: Master ES6+ features like arrow functions, destructuring, and modules
Understand asynchronous programming with Promises and async/await
Apply functional programming concepts in JavaScript
Optimize JavaScript applications for performance

title: Mobile App Development with Flutter
description: Build cross-platform mobile apps for iOS and Android with Google's Flutter framework.
learningOutcomes: Set up Flutter development environment
Create beautiful and responsive user interfaces with Flutter widgets
Manage state and data flow in Flutter applications
Publish apps to the Apple App Store and Google Play Store

title: Python for Data Science and AI
description: Learn Python programming for data analysis, visualization, and artificial intelligence.
learningOutcomes: Master Python programming fundamentals
Perform data analysis with NumPy and Pandas
Create data visualizations with Matplotlib and Seaborn
Implement machine learning algorithms for predictive modeling
